title: 01 = Zero one. [Ep. 09]
brief_description: Cinemagazine items including: 1. On-site manufacturing of foam plastic igloos useful for emergency housing. 2. Electrical powered feeding cart for barn-housed cattle. 3. Offset dye stamping machines for postage stamps doubling the capacity of current machines. 4. Flu vaccine production. 5. Stock cars.
